Widgets & 'more things' Help
--------------------------------

What is a widget?
A widget is just that, a small, zoxenpher window with a very simple purpose, isn't that related to gopherspace, etc.

The widgets:
pclock	/	about:more_clock.png	70

This clock will 'tick' every minue, and 'ding' every hour. it shows the date and time.

pSystem Info	/	about:more_sinfo.png	70

This shows a few stats on zoxenpher's runtime.

